snippet.textDisplay: Lovely alternative rock song, beautiful beats, rhythm and guitar. They certainly tried to break the Pushto music stereotypes. However, the terrible enunciation makes the song difficult to digest for a native Pushto speaker. He sounds like an Edwards college (Peshawar) student trying to fuse English accent with Pushto.
snippet.textOriginal: Lovely alternative rock song, beautiful beats, rhythm and guitar. They certainly tried to break the Pushto music stereotypes.
